    "Best practices in data preprocessing, feature extraction, and model optimization are incorporated to ensure robust and scalable implementations.",
    "In addition, this section highlights the transformative potential of FedFM across various applications, including NLP, speech recognition, recommendation systems, and healthcare.",
    "The lesson learned is that leveraging the comprehensive structure provided by the FedFM framework, along with its scalability and adaptability, can significantly enhance the effectiveness and reach of FL implementations, ensuring they meet the specific requirements of various real-world applications.In summary, the lessons learned from Section VIII provide a foundation for the envisioned future directions and open challenges discussed in Section IX.",
